accessdate=1 October 2011}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===DVD releases===\nBeginning in 2004, 20th Century Fox Home Entertainment began releasing the series on DVD in individual volumes, containing one two part episode per disc but later changed sometimes two separate episodes per disc. Later releases included either two discs or multiple episodes on one disc.\n\n====Original releases====\n(With two episodes per disc, except for ''Chillogy''):\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n|+[[DVD region code#1|Region 1]]\n! colspan=2|DVD title\n! Season(s)\n! Episode count\n! Release date\n! Episodes\n|-\n| style=background:#e96527|\n| ''The Haunted Mask II''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0002IQLE4 |title=Goosebumps \u2013 The Haunted Mask II (1995) |publisher=Amazon.com |date= |accessdate=2 October 2011}}</ref>\n| rowspan=3|2\n| rowspan=7|2\n| rowspan=4|7 September 2004\n| 30-31 (\"The Haunted Mask II\")\n|-\n| style=background:#0375be|\n| ''Night of the Living Dummy III''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0002IQLEE |title=Goosebumps \u2013 Night of the Dummy III (1995)|publisher=Amazon.com |date= |accessdate=2 October 2011}}</ref>\n| 43-44 (\"Night of the Living Dummy III\")\n|-\n| style=background:#fef200|\n| ''Welcome to Dead House''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0002IQLEY |title=Goosebumps \u2013 Welcome to Dead House (1995)|publisher=Amazon.com |date= |accessdate=2 October 2011}}</ref>\n| 39-40 (\"Welcome to Dead House\")\n|-\n| style=background:#55025a|\n| ''The Werewolf of Fever Swamp''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0002IQLFI|title=Goosebumps \u2013 The Werewolf of Fever Swamp (1995)|publisher=Amazon.com |date= |accessdate=2 October 2011}}</ref>\n| 1\n| 18-19 (\"The Werewolf of Fever Swamp\")\n|-\n| style=background:#016c96|\n| ''Cry of the Cat''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0007IO70O|title=Goosebumps \u2013 Cry of the Cat (1995)|publisher=Amazon.com |date= |accessdate=2 Octo