 the United States starting in 4 September 1995 and ending in 7 September 1998, with reruns on [[History of Freeform (TV channel)|Fox Family]] lasting until 6 September 1999 and 3 September 2001 respectively. Every October from 2007 to 2009, [[Cartoon Network]] aired the episodes. From 6 September 2011 until 1 September 2014, [[Discovery Family|The Hub]] broadcast the series. From 2013 onwards, '''[[Netflix]]''' has streamed all 74 episodes of the TV series on its online '''[[streaming service]]'''.\n\n==Home media==\n===VHS releases===\n====United Kingdom====\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Release name<br />\n! Release date<br />\n! Classifaction<br />\n! Publisher<br />\n! Format<br />\n! Language\n! Subtitles\n! Notes<br />\n! REF\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|| ''[[The Haunted Mask]]''\n|| 3 March 1997\n|| PG\n|| 20th Century Fox Home Entertainment\n|| PAL\n|| English\n|| None\n||\n||<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B00004CTYH/ |title=Goosebumps Haunted Mask [VHS]|publisher=amazon.co.uk |accessdate=1 October 2011}}</ref>\n|-\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|| ''[[The Werewolf of Fever Swamp]]''\n|| 23 February 1998\n|| Not Rated\n|| 20th Century Fox Home Entertainment\n|| PAL\n|| English\n|| None\n|| This episode is the only one given a 12 certificate in the UK due to its moderate, supernatural threat and heavy themes/depictions of animals being hunted and killed.\n||<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B0000574US |title=Goosebumps-Werewolf of Fever Swamp [VHS]|publisher=amazon.co.uk |accessdate=1 October 2011}}</ref>\n|-\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|| ''[[Night of the Living Dummy III]]''\n|| 1 October 1999\n|| PG\n|| 20th Century Fox Home Entertainment\n|| PAL\n|| English\n|| None\n||\n||<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B00004CV2A |title=Goosebumps Night of the Living Dummy [VHS]|publisher=amazon.co.uk |accessdate=1 October 2011}}</ref>\n|-\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|| ''[[Welcome to Camp Nightmare]