sdate=2 October 2011}}</ref>\n| rowspan=2|11 September 2007\n| 10 (\"Night of the Living Dummy II\") and 60 (\"Bride of the Living Dummy\")\n|-\n| style=background:#005baa|\n| ''Say Cheese and Die!''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/B000RPOCJS|title=Goosebumps: Say Cheese and Die|publisher=Amazon.com |date= |accessdate=2 October 2011}}</ref>\n| 15 (\"Say Cheese and Die\") and 62 (\"Say Cheese and Die... Again\")\n|}\n\n====Double features====\nOn 16 September 2008, twelve of the above sixteen discs were re-released in new double-feature sets, containing the same episodes as before.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Release name\n! UK release date<br />(region 2)\n! Australian release date<br />(region 4)\n! North American release date<br />(region 1)\n! Notes\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|| ''Night of the Living Dummy/<br />How I Got My Shrunken Head''\n||-\n||-\n|| 16 September 2008<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/B001B1UO9O/ |title=Goosebumps: Night of the Living Dummy/How I Got My Shrunken Head: Artist Not Provided: Movies & TV |publisher=Amazon.com |date= |accessdate=7 December 2009}}</ref>\n||\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|| ''Scary House/<br />Chillogy''\n|| \u2013\n|| \u2013\n|| 16 September 2008<ref>{{cite web|author=Latest activity 4 hours ago |url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/B001B1UOA8/ |title=Goosebumps: Scary House/Chillology: Artist Not Provided: Movies & TV |publisher=Amazon.com |date= |accessdate=7 December 2009}}</ref>\n||\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|| ''Perfect School/<br />My Best Friend Is Invisible''\n|| \u2013\n|| \u2013\n|| 16 September 2008<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/B001B1UO9Y/ |title=Goosebumps: Perfect School/My Best Friend Is Invisible: Artist Not Provided: Movies & TV |publisher=Amazon.com |date= |accessdate=7 December 2009}}</ref>\n||\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|| ''It Came from Beneath the Sink/<br />Deep Trouble''\n|| \u2013\n|| \u2013\n|| 16 September 2008<ref>{{cite web|